	,"x4freetext":[" The lithium targets used in"
		,"experiments were 99.994% pure 7Li metal, evaporated"
		,"in situ on a 0.0508 cm tantalum backing. Targets of"
		,"roughly 20 to 100 keV thickness for 8.7 MeV 3He."]
	}
